  <official_title>Active-controlled, Double-blind, Randomized, Sequential Escalating Dose Study to Assess Safety, Pharmacokinetics and Efficacy of 100, 150, and 200 mg Oral Risedronate Administered Monthly in Postmenopausal Women With Low Bone Mineral Density</official_title>
